name: Image Map
description: This module replaces an input, radio, or checkbox field with an interactive image where users can click on image regions to select one or more field options. Find the complete documentation and example instruments on GitHub

project-settings.name:
Enable console logging
If you check this box, logs will be written out to the console

system-settings.name:
Use API endpoint for urls
If you use SAML you may need to use the API endpoint for js urls in order for public (non-authenticated) browsers to be able to use this module on a survey
